The formula for $P(T \cup C)$ is $P(T) + P(C) - P(T \cap C)$. Substituting the given values, we have $P(T) + P(C) - 0.28 = 0.92$, which simplifies to $P(T) + P(C) = 1.20$.

## Step 5
